query: SELECT image_url, COUNT(DISTINCT property_id) as property_count, GROUP_CONCAT(DISTINCT property_id) as property_ids FROM property_images GROUP BY image_url HAVING COUNT(DISTINCT property_id) > 1 ORDER BY property_count DESC LIMIT 20;
